23、javascript由异常处理么？常用的异常处理有哪些？
try{
    //your code 
}catch(e){
    //while raise a error ,will exc this code
}
catch(e){
    //while raise a error,and pre catch has beed run  ,will exc this code
}
catch(e){
    //while raise a error,and pre catch has beed run  ,will exc this code
}final{
    //whether raise a error, this code will be run 
}

